{
  "text": "The influence of temperature over Cry proteins has been demonstrated by different authors. The Cry1Ac protein was degraded by exposure to temperature of 35 \u00b0C (27) . A reduction in Cry protein after 50 \u00b0C treatment was demonstrated by SDS-PAGE. They achieved temperature protection of the internal crystals by micro-capsulation [CITATION_1] .",
